        "@value": "https://nac-cna.ca/en/event/40423"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#title": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "Storgårds, Beethoven & Dvořák | and Élisabeth Pion's Debut | Nov 4 - 5, 2026 | Southam Hall"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#image": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "https://naccnaca-eventimages.s3.amazonaws.com/40423/metaadtemplate_8_(1)__event_1024__large.jpg"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#description": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "A few things to know...\n\n\n\tThis program celebrates John Storgårds’s first program as Music Director of the NAC Orchestra!\n\tFrom a musical meditation on the universe to a symphony overflowing with tranquil melodies, this program offers countless moments of beauty and calm.\n\tBeethoven wrote that he composed to express “what I have in my heart”—a sentiment brought to life in his tender, soul-stirring music for piano and orchestra.\n\n\nFeel your breath expand, and your mind unwind with the dreamy lyricism of Beethoven’s Fourth Piano Concerto. From..."
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns/fb#admins": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "728780803"
      }
    ],
